urlText: Lift at Bondi Junction Station not available between platforms 1/2 and the concourse
content:
The lift between platforms 1/2 and the concourse is temporarily out of service.
From Monday 27 February to Sunday 7 May, the lift will be closed for maintenance.
For accessible transport between Bondi Junction and the City, catch the 333 bus.
For accessible transport between Bondi Junction and Edgecliff, catch the 326, 327 or 328 bus.
If you need help, ask staff or phone 02 9379 4843.
